365
00:18:55.480 --> 00:18:56.990
Hikaru Ichigaya
Birthday: August 8, 1962
Age: 36   Blood type: A
<u>Profile</u>

366
00:19:01.910 --> 00:19:04.880
Dad, are you really going forward 
with the console release?

367
00:19:04.880 --> 00:19:05.890
Huh?!

368
00:19:05.890 --> 00:19:07.370
You bet I am!

369
00:19:07.650 --> 00:19:10.020
Isn't this what you wanted?

370
00:19:10.020 --> 00:19:11.910
I know you used to hate eroge.

371
00:19:11.910 --> 00:19:14.500
All that talk of working 
on something way bigger!

372
00:19:14.500 --> 00:19:16.850
A port wasn't what I had in mind.

373
00:19:16.850 --> 00:19:19.240
Now's your chance to strut your stuff!

374
00:19:19.240 --> 00:19:21.840
Things are about to get busy!

375
00:19:24.100 --> 00:19:25.510
Gaya-san!

376
00:19:24.100 --> 00:19:26.020
Ichigaya-san

377
00:19:24.100 --> 00:19:26.020
Voicemail        Sub-menu

378
00:19:26.020 --> 00:19:27.860
Ah, Gaya-san?

379
00:19:28.170 --> 00:19:30.190
I'm down! I'm down!

380
00:19:30.190 --> 00:19:31.680
Where are you right now?!

381
00:19:33.140 --> 00:19:35.380
See ya!

382
00:19:38.320 --> 00:19:41.810
I am a maid! Your very own maid!

383
00:19:41.810 --> 00:19:45.660
Cleaning, laundry, cooking, hm-hm-hmm!

384
00:19:46.750 --> 00:19:48.320
Mamoru-kun?

385
00:19:48.920 --> 00:19:50.810
Mamoru-kun!

386
00:19:51.410 --> 00:19:54.870
Hey, didn't you say you were going 
to steer clear of everyone?

387
00:19:54.870 --> 00:19:56.920
You don't count, Mamoru-kun!

388
00:19:56.920 --> 00:19:59.290
I can finally talk normally!

389
00:19:59.290 --> 00:20:02.100
Everyone's real fired up 
about the console game!

390
00:20:02.100 --> 00:20:03.350
How nice...

391
00:20:04.050 --> 00:20:05.400
Yeah.

392
00:20:05.400 --> 00:20:08.130
It's been a while since I've 
seen Dad so motivated.

393
00:20:08.130 --> 00:20:10.720
He's been out of the loop on 
company matters for a while.

394
00:20:11.840 --> 00:20:15.680
He can't keep up with all the changes 
bishojo games have been going through.

395
00:20:16.080 --> 00:20:18.730
All he does every night is go out drinking.

396
00:20:18.730 --> 00:20:22.000
I don't think he knows the first 
thing about Windows games.

397
00:20:22.000 --> 00:20:24.830
I guess the Windows phobia 
runs in the family!

398
00:20:29.240 --> 00:20:32.900
Which is why, with this console game offer,

399
00:20:32.900 --> 00:20:35.980
Dad must have wanted to show Kaori and 
Meiko that he could still be useful.

400
00:20:38.930 --> 00:20:39.780
Hey.

401
00:20:40.170 --> 00:20:42.040
What do you think about a console release?

402
00:20:42.040 --> 00:20:42.970
Huh?

403
00:20:44.940 --> 00:20:45.970
Never mind.

404
00:20:46.560 --> 00:20:48.630
I know I shouldn't ask you.

405
00:20:51.130 --> 00:20:53.860
A console release sounds great to me!

406
00:20:53.860 --> 00:20:55.650
I'd totally go for it!

407
00:20:55.650 --> 00:20:58.310
Everyone in the office 
is so excited about it!

408
00:20:59.320 --> 00:21:02.210
Are you really gonna stick 
to doing menial tasks?

409
00:21:02.210 --> 00:21:04.820
I thought you wanted to make a game.

410
00:21:05.940 --> 00:21:08.960
Deep down, I want to work on the game, too.

411
00:21:08.960 --> 00:21:12.750
But everyone else is trying so hard, 
without time travel or anything.

412
00:21:12.750 --> 00:21:17.360
It doesn't feel right for 
me to butt in on that.

413
00:21:19.510 --> 00:21:22.720
I'm just fine handling the chores!

414
00:21:22.720 --> 00:21:27.290
No matter the era I'm in, this 
is what it's like for me!

415
00:21:30.610 --> 00:21:32.370
Ow, ow...

416
00:21:34.510 --> 00:21:36.470
Ah, this sucks!

417
00:21:36.470 --> 00:21:38.970
All of my hard work!

418
00:21:40.270 --> 00:21:42.030
Come over
Kogyaru Club

419
00:21:40.570 --> 00:21:41.620
Wait...

420
00:21:42.040 --> 00:21:43.460
What's that?

421
00:21:43.460 --> 00:21:45.120
Where'd you get this garbage?

422
00:21:45.120 --> 00:21:48.910
That trash bag is from when
I cleaned the garage just now.

423
00:21:48.910 --> 00:21:52.080
This is a cosplay club run by Ichigaya.

